> sounds like your emergency flasher switch has popped apart.  the
> commonly do.  take it off and zip tie it tightly together.  things
> should start blinking again after that.


I did exactly that on my 73. Lasted until I gave the bus away.

There are lots of wires going into that switch, so pay attention to
which wire goes where if you have to unplug them to put the tie in.

